Muchidzidzo che[[Kupimanzvimbo]], [[gonyanhatu]] chiumbwa chine mativi matatu nemagonya matatu. Gonyanhatu chiumbwa chiri pamupanda we[[gonyazhinji]].  Gonyanhatu rine mikwava A, B, C rinonyorwa sezvizvi, ΔABC. 

==Mhando dzegonyanhatu==

Muchikamu chino tichataura pamusoro pemarudzi egonyanhatu; mhando dze[[gonyanhatu]] dzinotumidzwa mazita zvichienderana nekupimwa kwemativi uye magonya ari pakati paro. 

Kune [[gonyanhatu tsazakose]] (equilateral triangle) - iri rine mativi ose akaenza uye gonya nhatu dzose dzakaenzana. 

Kune [[gonyanhatu mutseyekwa]] (scalene triangle) - iri rine mativi ose ane nhambwe dzakasiyana uye gonya nhatu dzose dzakasiyana. Hazvinei [[gonyanhatu mutseyekwa]] agara nedivi ripi anotaridzika seanorerekera (kana kuwandira) kune rimwe divi nguva dzose. 

Kune [[gonyanhatu tsazamaviri]] (isosceles triangle) - iri rine mativi maviri akaenzana, negonya mbiri dzakaenzana. 

Kunoitawo [[gonyanhatu yemutwi]] (right-angled triangle) - iyi ine mativi maviri anosvika pamukwava une gonya re 90<sup>o</sup>.

